item.title: Need help!
item.dc:creator: @Javacisnotrecognized _^_
item.description:
@Javacisnotrecognized wrote:

Close all the browser windows you have open. Any kind of browser, firefox, IE, etc, close them all until the coffee icon at the bottom right dissapears. You may have to move your mouse over the icon for it to actually get off the toolbar once you’ve done that. Then restart the browser and load the webclient.
